---
title: Creamy Pancetta Gnocchi with Roasted Butternut and Apple
description: Chef Andre has created a beautiful harmony of flavours in this dish. Think caramelised butternut squash and apple in a creamy, silky sauce with savoury gnocchi and walnuts. Delicious!
